author: WCAX News
title: Police investigate shooting in Ellenburg
text:
ELLENBURG, N.Y. - New York state police are looking for the public's help in a shooting incident that happened last Friday in Ellenburg.
Police say a house was hit by shotgun fire early in the morning, and when the residents went out to investigate, another shot wounded Dominic Spooner, 21. He was hit by several shotgun pellets, but police described his injuries as minor.
